32typedef uint32_t tcp_seq;
33/*
34 * TCP header.
35 * Per RFC 793, September, 1981.
36 */
37struct tcphdr {
38 uint16_t th_sport; /* source port */
39 uint16_t th_dport; /* destination port */
40 tcp_seq th_seq; /* sequence number */
41 tcp_seq th_ack; /* acknowledgement number */
42 uint8_t th_offx2; /* data offset, rsvd */
43 uint8_t th_flags;
44 uint16_t th_win; /* window */
45 uint16_t th_sum; /* checksum */
46 uint16_t th_urp; /* urgent pointer */
47} UNALIGNED;
48
49#define TH_OFF(th) (((th)->th_offx2 & 0xf0) >> 4)
50
51/* TCP flags */
52#define TH_FIN 0x01
53#define TH_SYN 0x02
54#define TH_RST 0x04
55#define TH_PUSH 0x08
56#define TH_ACK 0x10
57#define TH_URG 0x20
58#define TH_ECNECHO 0x40 /* ECN Echo */
59#define TH_CWR 0x80 /* ECN Cwnd Reduced */
60
61
62#define TCPOPT_EOL 0
63#define TCPOPT_NOP 1
64#define TCPOPT_MAXSEG 2
65#define TCPOLEN_MAXSEG 4
66#define TCPOPT_WSCALE 3 /* window scale factor (rfc1323) */
67#define TCPOPT_SACKOK 4 /* selective ack ok (rfc2018) */
68#define TCPOPT_SACK 5 /* selective ack (rfc2018) */
69#define TCPOPT_ECHO 6 /* echo (rfc1072) */
70#define TCPOPT_ECHOREPLY 7 /* echo (rfc1072) */
71#define TCPOPT_TIMESTAMP 8 /* timestamp (rfc1323) */
72#define TCPOLEN_TIMESTAMP 10
73#define TCPOLEN_TSTAMP_APPA (TCPOLEN_TIMESTAMP+2) /* appendix A */
74#define TCPOPT_CC 11 /* T/TCP CC options (rfc1644) */
75#define TCPOPT_CCNEW 12 /* T/TCP CC options (rfc1644) */
76#define TCPOPT_CCECHO 13 /* T/TCP CC options (rfc1644) */
77#define TCPOPT_SIGNATURE 19 /* Keyed MD5 (rfc2385) */
78#define TCPOLEN_SIGNATURE 18
79#define TCP_SIGLEN 16 /* length of an option 19 digest */
80#define TCPOPT_SCPS 20 /* SCPS-TP (CCSDS 714.0-B-2) */
81#define TCPOPT_UTO 28 /* tcp user timeout (rfc5482) */
82#define TCPOLEN_UTO 4
83#define TCPOPT_TCPAO 29 /* TCP authentication option (rfc5925) */
84#define TCPOPT_MPTCP 30 /* MPTCP options */
85#define TCPOPT_FASTOPEN 34 /* TCP Fast Open (rfc7413) */
86#define TCPOPT_EXPERIMENT2 254 /* experimental headers (rfc4727) */
87
88#define TCPOPT_TSTAMP_HDR \
89 (TCPOPT_NOP<<24|TCPOPT_NOP<<16|TCPOPT_TIMESTAMP<<8|TCPOLEN_TIMESTAMP)
